07:42:00,000 --> 07:48:00,000
export ACCOUNT_ID equals aws sts get-caller-identity query Account output text.
export REGION equals us-east-1.
export START equals date minus d 30 days ago plus YYYY-MM-DD.
export END equals date plus YYYY-MM-DD.

79
07:48:00,000 --> 07:54:00,000
Verify your current storage spend.
aws ce get-cost-and-usage with filter for S3, RDS, ElastiCache, and ECR.

80
07:54:00,000 --> 08:00:00,000
Write this number down. It is your baseline for Series six.

