82
08:06:00,000 --> 08:12:00,000
First, find your most expensive buckets.

83
08:12:00,000 --> 08:18:00,000
Loop through all S3 buckets.
For each bucket, get the total size in gigabytes.
Calculate the estimated monthly cost at the Standard tier.

84
08:18:00,000 --> 08:24:00,000
Sort by cost descending.
The top result is your most expensive bucket.

85
08:24:00,000 --> 08:30:00,000
Now check the storage class distribution for each bucket.

86
08:30:00,000 --> 08:36:00,000
List all objects. Count how many are in Standard,
